body:
Comment 5: 
printdir.cmd batch file is generated by TestWinSplitListTestsAreValid on the fly (see
the source). If you insert fmt.Printf statements to debug, you should be able to find
out what is going wrong. Are you using standard cmd.exe ?

Alex

PS: You don't need to have all.bat complete successfully to use Go. Running make.bat is
enough. all.bat runs make.bat plus execute all tests.
